Evaluation d'un troisieme projet
            routier - Mauritanie

abstracts.cdata!:
The project would consist of the
            following: (a) technical assistance to the Ministry of
            Equipment; (b) purchase of highway equipment for maintenance
            and betterment works; (c) continuation of a betterment
            program on about 365 km of roads; (d) feasibility study and
            detailed engineering for construction of the Rosso-Boghe
            road (200 km).
